sequenceDiagram

participant User
participant CLI
participant Runner
participant Backend
participant Pytest

User->>CLI: run command

CLI->>CLI: parse args

CLI->>CLI: create ExecutionRequest

CLI->>Runner: run(request)

Runner->>Backend: execute(request)

Backend->>Pytest: subprocess.run()

Pytest-->>Backend: exit_code, stdout

Backend-->>Runner: ExecutionResult

Runner-->>CLI: ExecutionResult

CLI-->>User: display summary
